From 5232cc814b6bc7f0668d4f0328d0fd0de0db7022 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:02:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(backend): organizer wallet, payouts & money management

Money flow: paid payment -> organizer credited (gross - fee, held) ->
released after event end + grace hours (if still paid) -> organizer
requests payout -> admin approves/mark-paid (manual for now).

- Migrations: organizer_wallets, wallet_transactions (ledger), payouts,
  platform_settings (fee/grace/min defaults: 5%, 48h, 10000 XAF).
- Models: OrganizerWallet, WalletTransaction, Payout, PlatformSetting;
  User/Payment relations + Payment::updated hook (idempotent credit).
- WalletService: credit/reverse/release/balances/payout lifecycle.
- Console command 'payouts:release-held' scheduled daily.
- Controllers: WalletController (organizer), AdminPayoutController (admin).
- Resources + routes (organizer wallet + admin payouts/settings).
